contentrichtext.text: {{wiktionary}} '''FDL''' is an abbreviation for: *[[Federation of Italian Liberals]], more commonly known in Italian as ''Federazione dei Liberali Italiani'' *[[Fiber Delay Line]] *[[File Definition Language]], in [[OpenVMS]] *[[Telecine#Line array CCD|Film Digital Line]], Model [[Spirit_DataCine#FDL_60|FDL60]] and FDL90 [[Telecine]] from [[Robert Bosch GmbH]], [[Fernseh]] Div. *[[Firedoglake]], a political blog *[[Fleur-de-lis]] *Flexible and Distributed Learning see [[e-learning]] *[[Flexor digitorum longus muscle|Flexor digitorum longus]] muscle *[[Flow Definition Language]] *[[Fond du Lac]], several places in the United States and Canada *[[Food, Drug, and Liquor]], as in retail channels for selling alcohol beverages. *[[Foresight Linux|Foresight Desktop GNU/Linux]] *[[Fossa dei Leoni]] *''Frame Display Lists'', an aspect of the [[Gecko (layout engine)|Gecko]] API *[[GNU Free Documentation License]] *[[US Airforce Flight Dynamics Laboratory]] '''FDL''' can also be in reference to: *The [[GE FDL]] series of diesel engines {{disambiguation}}
